Title: Skintruth Manicure Cuticle Massage Cream
Description: Hand care is an important aspect of personal hygiene. Making the hands soft and supple and maintaining their softness requires constant cleansing and hydration. The cuticles often are neglected spots due to lack of time to tend to them. Hard and torn cuticles can be painful and embarrassing at the same time. Skintruth has introduced a wide range of products to pamper and caress your hands. The Cuticle Massage Cream from Skintruth is an enriched hand cream that helps in tending to your cuticles. This Cuticle Massage Cream is enhanced with the goodness cocoa butter, almond oil and rosemary. This Cuticle Massage Cream gently softens the cuticle prior to removing it. The cream also conditions the nail bed to keep the nail healthy. Replete with antioxidants like vitamins A, C and E cocoa butter not only moisturizes the hands but also protects it from the adverse effects of free radicals. Cocoa butter is also effective in retaining the moisture of the skin. Almond oil is known for the abundance of vitamin E in it. This rich oil is skin rejuvenator as it softens and smoothens the skin along with reducing the effect of skin irritations. The healing vitamins in the almond oil hydrates dry skin and strengthens brittle nails. These qualities of almond oil stimulate the growth of healthy nails. Rosemary is yet another natural ingredient infused in the Cuticle Massage Cream from Skintruth that moisturizes and refreshes the skin with its astringent and hydrating characteristics. It also helps in regenerating skin cells and stimulating blood circulation in the skin leaving the skin glowing with a healthy shine. Directions to use: • Wash clean your hands. • Pat dry the hands of excess water. • Apply an adequate amount of Cuticle Massage Cream to your hands and gently massage it into your hands until it is completely absorbed.
CategoryName: Health and Beauty>Mens Grooming>Body and Skin Care>Moisturizers and Creams

Title: Skintruth Hand Creamy Cuticle Remover with Lavender
Description: Cuticles are thin skin on your nail ridges that protect your nail beds from infections. But hardened and torn cuticles on hands and toes can become painful and embarrassing at times. Removing cuticles can also be a task at times if they are too dry and hard. Skintruth has brought about products that can be used to pamper and caress your hands and feet with. The Creamy Cuticle Remover from the hand care range of Skintruth products is a cuticle removing cream. This cream that is infused with antiseptic properties will help in gently softening and dissolving dead and damaged cuticles so that they can be easily removed without pain. The Creamy Cuticle Remover from Skintruth is enriched with lavender extracts. Lavender is known to have antiseptic and antifungal properties that will help in keeping your hands free of infections. It is also effective in making your hands feel relieved and soothed. You can use this Cuticle Remover to soften the hardened cuticles so that they can be removed with no fuss. Using the cuticle remover also helps in removing the cuticle without having to cut it which might cause infections. Useful tips: • Clean your hands by washing them with water. • Apply an adequate amount of the Skintruth Creamy Cuticle Remover to your nails making sure that the cuticles are covered. • Allow the cuticles to soften, use a cuticle pusher to push back the cuticles. • Wash your hands thoroughly to wash away the cuticle removes from your hand.

Skintruth Eye Makeup Remover
Description: If you have experienced red eyes soon after you clean your eye makeup, then its time you change the method of cleaning your makeup. The eye area is very sensitive and delicate and thus requires a lot of attention. Skintruth Eye Makeup Remover cleans every bit of eye makeup without harming your skin. This makeup remover is suitable for all skin types including those who have sensitive skin. The soothing Skintruth eye makeup remover refreshes and tones the skin around your eyes by providing re-hydration. It helps to remove even the waterproof makeup from your eye region. The key component in this eye makeup remover is Horse Chestnut. Found in the Himalayas, horse chestnut is a good toner and helps in refreshing the eye area. It also promotes even complexion and also provides a firming effect on skin. The goodness of this ingredient makes this eye remover suitable for sensitive skin. Now indulge in no rinse, hassle-free removal of makeup from your eyes, including those with long-wearing and waterproof formulas. Direction for Use: Dab the eye makeup remover onto a cotton pad.
